channel.title: Relive -317- ECO
channel.description: Relive recreates memories of 2006, A great economy, a great player base, and most important, Great staff. This server is one of the best i have played, because it takes me back to old rsps, the good 317's that actually had a good economy. You have to earn your items, You start out with enough to get you through, but after that, you're on your own! One of the best economy's on a 317 right now, of course, it is not that hard to get items. Hope to see you there? :cool: hosted on 24/7 vps -Website- http://www.reliveserver.com/index.php <--- Visit us! :cool: :cool:
